Hosted the last event of the year, and it was truly memorable!✨
Had the privilege of being part of the premium card launch by @tajmahalmumbai X @hsbc_in Congratulations to Mr. Dave and Mr. Chhatwal for such a remarkable collaboration. The evening was filled with beautiful moments and I got to share the stage with some of my favorites, @ananyapanday and @gaurikhan 🤍
And let's not forget the soulful sitar performance by @rishabsmusic it was truly mesmerizing. @sanyamalhotra_ you're even more stunning in person! 
 
Thank you @tajmahalmumbai @ryanritesh and your entire team for the amazing hospitality, you always make us feel special. Here's to a successful event and an even more successful year ahead!
Having my daughter @deannemarshall_ by my side made the evening even more meaningful and special! 💗💗

Thanks @anaitashroffadajania for styling me in the gorgeous @shantanunikhil  outfit.

latestPosts.caption:
May you were a whirlwind of magic, movement and mangoes 🥭💫

1.  Hosted the stunning project reveal event for @rustomjee_spaces , love being part of Mumbai’s top real estate brand😍

	2. Alibaug fam time 🫶

	3.	WE ARE LIVERPOOL. WE ARE CHAMPIONS. Say it louder! 🔴 #YNWA

	4. Deanne left for summer school with her tiny backpack, big emotions. Heart =Full 💛

	5. Dressed like a rockstar, danced like no one’s watching – Guns N’ Roses LIVE was epic. 🤘

	6. Birthday morning rituals with our Parsi Ses, flowers, coconut, and so much love. 🌼

7 and 8 Birthday evening was all things joy, laughter, hugs and cake — 🥂

	9. One of my current gym fits lately. Moving my body, lifting my spirits 💪 @kore.with.karina @korefit_in 

	10. To my brother, the Captain — may the wind always be in your favour. 🌊🧭

	11. Mango season (my favourite) means time for my signature Mango Tart.

12. Caught a moment in Mumbai Traffic.

(Parizad Kolah, Event Host, May Dump, Alibaug, Liverpool, Mango Season, May Mood, Outfit Diaries, Monthly Dump, May Recap)
